00:31:12,066 --> 00:31:14,606
Just like there's an install
application MDM command,


681
00:31:14,766 --> 00:31:17,086
there's now an Install
Media MDM command


682
00:31:17,656 --> 00:31:20,766
where if it's a managed
iBookstore book,


683
00:31:20,766 --> 00:31:22,826
you'll just specify
the iTunes store ID.


