ID that's under your control


687
00:31:32,316 --> 00:31:35,236
so that you can uniquely
identify each enterprise book


688
00:31:35,236 --> 00:31:37,236
that's being installed
and its kind


689
00:31:38,036 --> 00:31:40,106
and then the matching
remove media command.


690
00:31:42,606 --> 00:31:44,256
There are a few limitations.


691
00:31:45,026 --> 00:31:48,046
Just like managed apps, is
requires the app installation


692
00:31:48,046 --> 00:31:49,116
and the end enrollment, right,


693
00:31:49,116 --> 00:31:50,696
to be able to install
managed books.


